                "invention-title": [
                    "Load shedding adjusting method and system based on hydrogen energy storage and hydrogen fuel automobile",
                    "一种基于氢储能和氢燃料汽车的切负荷调整方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a load shedding adjustment method and system based on hydrogen energy storage and a hydrogen fuel automobile. According to a preset time interval, regularly obtaining operation data of each power grid node of the power distribution network, set data of fuel cells currently participating in scheduling and set data of hydrogen fuel vehicles currently participating in scheduling; inputting the operation data, the fuel cell set data and the hydrogen fuel vehicle set data into a preset energy scheduling model, so that the energy scheduling model calculates the power supply efficiency of each fuel cell and each hydrogen fuel vehicle to the power distribution network, and further determines a first cut load capacity of each power grid node of the power distribution network; and controlling the power distribution network to perform load shedding adjustment according to the first load shedding amount of each power grid node. According to the invention, the hydrogen energy technology is integrated into the electric power infrastructure, so that the power supply elasticity and recovery efficiency of the power distribution network in an extreme environment are effectively improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种基于氢储能和氢燃料汽车的切负荷调整方法及系统，所述方法包括：在配电网恢复周期内，根据预设的时间间隔定时获取配电网的各个电网节点的运行数据、当前参与调度的燃料电池集合数据以及当前参与调度的氢燃料汽车集合数据；将所述运行数据、燃料电池集合数据以及氢燃料汽车集合数据输入至预设的能源调度模型，以使所述能源调度模型计算出各个燃料电池和各个氢燃料汽车对所述配电网的供电效率，进而确定所述配电网的各个电网节点的第一切负荷量；根据所述各个电网节点的第一切负荷量控制所述配电网进行切负荷调整。本发明通过将氢能技术整合进电力基础设施，有效提高了配电网在极端环境下的供电弹性和恢复效率。"
                }
            ]
